rules.description: Remap keys to use Dvorak keyboard layout
Change fn + W/A/S/D to Arrow Keys
Change fn + I/J/K/L to Arrow Keys
Change fn + shift (QWERTY: ; semicolon | Dvork: s) to Delete Forward
Change fn + (QWERTY: ; semicolon | Dvork: s) to Backspace
Change fn + (QWERTY: ' quote | Dvork: - hyphen) to Delete Forward
Shift-Delete to Delete-Forward (deletes next character, use both shift keys to bypass)
Option-Shift-Delete to Option-Delete-Forward (deletes next word, use both shift keys to bypass)
Command-Shift-Delete to Ctrl-K (deletes rest of line, use both shift keys to bypass)
